### Create a high-difficulty event
POST http://localhost:8000/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Mountain Trail Restoration",
  "description": "Advanced physical work restoring hiking trails in mountainous terrain",
  "location": "Blue Mountain Preserve",
  "date_start": "2024-02-01T08:00:00",
  "date_end": "2024-02-01T16:00:00",
  "difficulty": "hard",
  "duration_minutes": 480,
  "proposed_points": 100,
  "max_participants": 10,
  "organization_id": 3
}

### Update an existing event
PUT http://localhost:8000/events/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Beach Cleanup - Extended Hours",
  "description": "Help clean up the local beach with extended hours for more impact",
  "max_participants": 25,
  "proposed_points": 60
}

### Partial update with only some fields
PUT http://localhost:8000/events/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "location": "New Food Bank Location, 456 Oak Ave",
  "max_participants": 25
}

### Update with all optional fields
PUT http://localhost:8000/events/3
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Mountain Trail Restoration - Volunteer Day",
  "description": "Join us for a day of trail restoration with improved planning",
  "location": "Blue Mountain Preserve - North Trail",
  "date_start": "2024-02-01T07:30:00",
  "date_end": "2024-02-01T16:30:00",
  "difficulty": "hard",
  "duration_minutes": 540,
  "proposed_points": 120,
  "final_points": 120,
  "max_participants": 12,
  "status": "open"
}

### Update event status
PUT http://localhost:8000/events/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "closed"
}

### Close an event (stop accepting applications)
POST http://localhost:8000/events/1/close

### Delete an event
DELETE http://localhost:8000/events/1
